March 2, 1970 No. 18,

Orig.

Illinois v. Missouri. [For earlier orders herein, see, e. g., 386 U. S. 902.]

Report of Special Master received and ordered filed. Exceptions, if any, with supporting briefs may be filed on or before June 1, 1970. Reply briefs, if any, to such exceptions may be filed on or before July 15, 1970.
